metadata.name: Erythrophobia
metadata.description:
“I shy away because I know you never blush. I blush because you never shy away.”

NFT format: 5000 x 2812 px / PNG / 21.1MB
OMG page: https://alexandru-crisan.com/projects/omg/

Note that this NFT is backed by an unframed archival pigment art print on paper at museum standard, 100 x 100 cm, signed by the author, that the winner of the auction may redeem once the price point of ETH 10 has been reached/exceeded. Any sale bellow this price point, and any subsequent sales of the NFT on secondary markets, will not generate any contractual obligations for the artist.
